Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you probably often go on remote shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In "stroll-around-town" variety, TV talents go to restaurants ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,... where they have to get filming permission. - Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll go "Is it ok if we shoot here?". - "Are you ok with cameras?".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they get permission, they'll go "OK~!". - All the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I have a theory that's related to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"If, in a stroll-around-town type variety where you have to go ask for filming permission, ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"... your co-host went inside and didn't return no matter how long you wait, ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"... you'll ultimately assume the worst!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about as meaningless a theory as they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"If, in a stroll-around-town type variety where you have to go ask for filming permission, ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"... your co-host went inside and didn't return no matter how long you wait, ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"... you'll ultimately assume the worst!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The comedy duo Kaeru-tei makes up the target (left) & instigator (right) of our investigation this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this point, they've participated in a stroll-around-town type shoot for around an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:14.49,Comments,,0,0,0,,They're shooting diligently!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The nuts taste great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah, a Chinese restaurant! - Chinese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're delicious, these hole-in-the-wall shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our setting will be this Chinese restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for your success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's hyped herself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:41.15,Comments,,0,0,0,,They're this far away from the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How'll it go? Ah, are they even open? Seems they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.09,Comments,,0,0,0,,Pretty far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's inside! - Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her first time asking for shooting permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakano is worried for his partner, since she's not experienced with this type of shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.57,Comments,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,5 minutes pass since Iwakura entered the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.98,Comments,,0,0,0,,That's long! - 5 minutes is long for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it normally take this long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 10 minutes pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:20.22,Comments,,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This has gone beyond "she has trouble since it's her first time". - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.50,Comments,,0,0,0,,You'd get worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.03,Comments,,0,0,0,,I want him to go save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken quite long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,By this time I'm getting a bit worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go have a glimpse? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.17,Comments,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can even see them from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:41.24,Comments,,0,0,0,,She could've simply set up an "I've already eaten before you" kind of joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He moves to get a grasp of the situation inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When he opens the door to the restaurant ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:49.39,Comments,,0,0,0,,Eh, that's scary! - Terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,... he will find the scene of a scuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are even bloodstains on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.36,Comments,,0,0,0,,Creating suspense?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, Iwakura's possessions are all over the palce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:58.53,Comments,,0,0,0,,The staff at this show is messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How will Nakano react?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.63,Comments,,0,0,0,,That's terrifying! - I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.60,Comments,,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.24,Comments,,0,0,0,,Terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.58,Comments,,0,0,0,,Ah, the owner's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.25,Comments,,0,0,0,,But that's all the more scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with a TV show for TBS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're walking around, filming in this area ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,... in the hopes of visiting some restaurants that look promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that my partner came to visit you moments ago ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.34,Comments,,0,0,0,,Scary ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know? Well ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:43.87,Comments,,0,0,0,,SCARY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't someone come here earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.91,Comments,,0,0,0,,Eh, he's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, but someone did come in here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:55.89,Comments,,0,0,0,,I'd be fearing for my life if I was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ... is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ominous owner feigns ignorance ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,... and for an instant he backs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His face is saying "Damn, I screwed up".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But one person did come in here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching the entire time, and she didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.61,Comments,,0,0,0,,No ... !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Nakano hangs on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a 2nd floor? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there customer seating in the 2nd floor? - Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.72,Comments,,0,0,0,,Why does he talk like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you perhaps show me the inside of the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:38.76,Comments,,0,0,0,,Amazing! He's trying to look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be too much trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. - Ah ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did no one come here earlier? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No one came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.54,Comments,,0,0,0,,Scary! - To be repeatedly told "No one came here" ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But now ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.45,Comments,,0,0,0,,A voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- ... what's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? - What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.86,Comments,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \N- What kind of shoot is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What sound? - This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you on about? - Could you just let me check?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:11.33,Comments,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! \N- You gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Check? Check what? - The back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear an unusual voice from back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem. - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.33,Comments,,0,0,0,,Is he going to go back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bullshit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.50,Comments,,0,0,0,,This is so scary ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you? - Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my store. - I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? - Ex- ... excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.51,Comments,,0,0,0,,Amazing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.52,Comments,,0,0,0,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What a reaction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:50.17,Comments,,0,0,0,,What was that about just now? - It was like from a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably come off even if you just open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.57,Comments,,0,0,0,,You're a brave one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work. - Don't just "Good work" me, that guy was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so damn scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.55,Comments,,0,0,0,,Now he looks kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At first I thought maybe she was preparing some kind of joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.96,Comments,,0,0,0,,Just as you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But the wait kept getting longer and she wouldn't come out ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,... so I figured she must've been trapped somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I went inside to find this scary guy waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.90,Comments,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on to the next instigator & target pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:33.14,Comments,,0,0,0,,This is quite the pair! - Are they gonna be alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollywood Zakoshisyoh & Chance Oshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.51,Comments,,0,0,0,,Will Oshiro be ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Oshiro going to be alright here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them have little experience with stroll-around-town variety ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,... but at this point they've already been filming for around an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An exaggeration of Doi Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Doi Takako, I told you it was Renaissance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading in! Like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.38,Comments,,0,0,0,,The shoot looks like a lot of fun though!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisyoh went inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.62,Comments,,0,0,0,,Oshiro's going to be hopeless. - Yeah, Chance is not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he can get permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but this is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:24.59,Comments,,0,0,0,,When panicking he's capable of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance is fully enjoying this variety shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,10 minutes pass without Shisyoh returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.23,Comments,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Shisyoh get caught up in something? - Right ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go check on him? - I'll go have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisyoh's taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This time ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,... the staff that's part of this shoot will also disappear one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.79,Comments,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll investigate how Chance will react once he's the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on in there? - It's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're taking quite long, is it ok if we also go take a look? - Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait here a moment. - Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the director & cameraman also head inside, completing our preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.57,Comments,,0,0,0,,All of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,5 minutes pass since he's been made to wait all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.52,Comments,,0,0,0,,What will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're taking long! Maybe I should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they had their lights punched out by a dodgy employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Maybe that Chinese restaurant ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.16,Comments,,0,0,0,,"punched their lights out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,... is a front for organized crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do Chinese restaurants like that even exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way the very first restaurant ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,... in a shopping district in Gotokuji would be a shady place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:45.41,Comments,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As no one returns from the restaurant ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,... he theorizes that this hole-in-the-wall Chinese restaurant is involved in organized crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.12,Comments,,0,0,0,,I've never heard anyone say that! - Now he's eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He listens closely to get a feel for the situation inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.76,Comments,,0,0,0,,He won't go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah this is scary, what should I do ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.73,Comments,,0,0,0,,No choice but to go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't bring himself to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Chance, unable to muster the courage to go inside, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.21,Comments,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,... buys tea from a convenience store ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.91,Comments,,0,0,0,,Eh, why? - Why would he ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,... and bread from a nearby bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.82,Comments,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He opens the door just a little to get a glimpse of the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:34.12,Comments,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is scary ... super scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.56,Comments,,0,0,0,,I told you Chance is not normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the scary one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He walks up and down in front of the store to get his thoughts in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:01.48,Comments,,0,0,0,,You've gotta go! \N- Yeah, something clearly happened in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.53,Comments,,0,0,0,,Everything in disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so scary ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This time the owner of the restaurant won't even show himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there was definitely a scuffle here ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There was definitely- UWAAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.55,Comments,,0,0,0,,That sure is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisyoh ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.39,Comments,,0,0,0,,Move the chair at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisyoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.47,Comments,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisyoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisyoh!! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.11,Comments,,0,0,0,,Surely you can tell what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.85,Comments,,0,0,0,,He still can't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ... are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it ... an employee here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I was so scared, I was sure you'd gotten involved with someone shady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.92,Comments,,0,0,0,,I mean surely you can figure it out by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this to you? The owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.13,Comments,,0,0,0,,He thinks this is organized crime after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah, no way! WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I GOT IT! I GOT IT, ALRIGHT?! JUST WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,JUST WAIT! WAIT WAIT WAIT WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT A SECOND! JUST WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.64,Comments,,0,0,0,,He's taking out money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,IT'S ALL OK, JUST WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.61,Comments,,0,0,0,,Money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I GOT IT! JUST WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.39,Comments,,0,0,0,,He laid out money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,7000 yen! I counted 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why 7000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:51.03,Comments,,0,0,0,,That's just a bit over 1000 yen per person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M SO SORRY! We were just filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm ... I'm really sorry! I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they rude to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! NO WAIT! PLEASE JUST WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait! I have someone I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl I want to confess to! Please wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even been to an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point we reveal everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.38,Comments,,0,0,0,,He wants to go to an amusement park! - What should he wait for, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:14.82,Comments,,0,0,0,,But he wants to go to an amusement park! \N- With the girl he loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply thought I had no choice but to go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but you couldn't bring yourself to do it for the longest time! - It was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to get stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was it for me. My life would end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought "So this is how it ends".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"At last they put me on TV more and then I get killed"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just my life, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the girl Chance wanted to confess to is the 3 o'clock heroine, Yumecchi.
